orm=\"biblScope\">8.365</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg005.perseus-grc1:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Ven.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">62</biblScope> </bibl>: c. dat., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stick to,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στομίοισι πέριξ ἐ. γαστρός,</foreign> of leeches when swallowed, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0022.tlg002:509\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nic.\">Nic.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Al.\">Al.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">509</biblScope> </bibl>: perh. related to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπανθέω.</foreign> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n38642.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of Time, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πουλὺς ἐ. αἰών</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">had passed,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> R.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.276</biblScope></bibl>. (Cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατ-, παρ-;</foreign> also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνήνοθε</foreign>: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπανήνοθε</foreign> shd. perh. be restored in signf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}